{"tid":1051182,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"中國永諾 YN450 4G 無反相機結合智能手機　可裝 Canon EF 鏡頭","createTime":"2019-03-07T11:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T09:59:11.000Z","uid":50534,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"324df2be44884dc1e9a01afb5e7bf1e501ab12d6","tid":1051182,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/06/yn450-4g/dc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2Fyn450-4g%2Fdc%2F&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=52ddc762\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/06/yn450-4g/dc/</a><br />\n中國永諾 YN450 4G 無反相機結合智能手機　可裝 Canon EF 鏡頭<br />\nLogin<br />\n<br />\n中國攝影器材品牌永諾一直以來，都以平價第三方鏡頭等為主要產品。如今，他們正式推出一款採用 Android 系統的「智能無反相機」YN450 4G ，當中更採用 Canon EF 轉接環，用家可自行交換鏡頭。這款相機在本屆日本 CP+ 攝影器材展覽上登場，引起一眾科技媒體登場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Yongnuo_YN450_1-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FYongnuo_YN450_1-640x360.jpg&h=5e41dfb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Yongnuo_YN450_3-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FYongnuo_YN450_3-640x360.jpg&h=d9e1fad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Yongnuo_YN450_2-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FYongnuo_YN450_2-640x360.jpg&h=77896b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYN450 4G 以智能系統為主要賣點，採用 Android 7.1 系統，同時配有 3GB RAM 及 32GB ROM 。在熒幕介面上，可見它採用相機常見的調節環設計，極具特色。相機採用 1,600 萬像的 M43 片幅，同時支援 4K 錄影功能。除採用 5 吋 1080p 觸控熒幕外，更附有一個 800 萬像的自拍鏡頭及支援 4G 網絡，背面看起來十足一部智能手機。而電池容量則為 4,000 mAh 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有分析指，這款相機因為具備 4G 功能及 Android 系統，讓這部相機成為不少 YouTuber 及 Vlogger 進行直播時的選擇。事實上，早於去年 10 月，永諾已公布這款相機，當時更舉行命名比賽。而這部相機將於下個月，於中國率先發售，不過永諾尚未正式公布海外發售詳情。"},{"pid":"1c3da454325a25f25e1a8e8495a6adb9afdb00e2","tid":1051182,"uid":18955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T14:21:57.000Z","msg":"帶smart phone功能嘅相機？"},{"pid":"a9d964537f5467d886c5ebd0d8ec8a2c5b85ef72","tid":1051182,"uid":1482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:08:03.000Z","msg":"買鏡頭送電話"},{"pid":"9f11cc2f7a2d590640082ef9abc737f3e57fe845","tid":1051182,"uid":175630,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"採用 Android 7.1 系統，同時配有 3GB RAM 及 32GB ROM........................"},{"pid":"6c94453a188915e496bf242be12d4029c5e99c9e","tid":1051182,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:26:16.000Z","msg":"m43 35mm youtuber影衫鈕<br />\n<br />\n定係用自拍鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24da5610bdc2b639b57c7f3f76cd5118db32e590","tid":1051182,"uid":45498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T22:58:09.000Z","msg":"支那不了"},{"pid":"6196dc743eadefc20cee93ef65464169365665e1","tid":1051182,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"我都諗過Canon Nikon出手機可以接佢地d鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36a2d10fd987d2ad485a8652c792522b6d02096","tid":1051182,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6196dc743eadefc20cee93ef65464169365665e1","tid":1051182,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"我都諗過Canon Nikon出手機可以接佢地d鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"D610 user, 有Full frame smartphone 即狗沖"},{"pid":"20637a0f72a6202a72aaab103f5f903aaf902ec7","tid":1051182,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"維修唔係因為爆Mon，而係因為爆鏡"}]}